    <p>Open People Studio partners with operators who need AI to create clarity, not chaos. Our flagship pilot is Snow White Laundry (SWL) in St. John’s, Newfoundland and Labrador — a hospitality venture running cortex() across build, finance, and operations before the first plate is served.</p>
    <p>When I am not in the studio, I am documenting the Operator OS, testing new alignment rituals, and mentoring founders inside the Genesis Centre network.</p>

